<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ subject }}</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .logo-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        
        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
            height: auto;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 25px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .header .subtitle {
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .urgency-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        
        .urgency-badge.urgent {
            background-color: #dc3545;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .urgency-badge.important {
            background-color: #fd7e14;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .urgency-badge.normal {
            background-color: #198754;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 30px 25px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .highlight-box {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #e3f2fd, #f8f9ff);
            border: 1px solid #2196f3;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .highlight-box::before {
            content: "📋";
            font-size: 20px;
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            right: 20px;
        }
        
        .modules-count {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1976d2;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .owner-name {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        
        .main-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.6);
        }
        
        .motivation-text {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #495057;
        }
        
        .signature {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        
        .signature-name {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px 25px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .footer-warning {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer-warning strong {
            color: #856404;
        }
        
        .stats-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            margin: 20px 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
        }
        
        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .stat-number {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #667eea;
            display: block;
        }
        
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 10px;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            
            .content, .header {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            
            .stats-container {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <!-- Logo -->
        <div class="logo-container">
            {% if logo_cid is defined and logo_cid is not null %}
                <img src="cid:{{ logo_cid }}" alt="EDF Logo" class="logo">
            {% else %}
                <img src="{{ absolute_url(asset('images/logos/edf.png')) }}" alt="EDF Logo" class="logo">
            {% endif %}
        </div>
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Rappel de validation</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">Carnet de compagnonnage</div>
            
            {% if urgency_level.text %}
                <div class="urgency-badge {{ urgency_level.class }}">
                    {{ urgency_level.text }}
                </div>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
        
        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Bonjour {{ mentor_firstname }},
            </div>
            
            <!-- Highlight box with main information -->
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <div class="modules-count">
                    {{ number_text|title }} {{ modules_text }} {{ verb_text }} en attente de validation
                </div>
                <div>
                    dans le carnet de compagnonnage de <span class="owner-name">{{ owner_fullname }}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Stats - Visualisation moderne du nombre de modules en attente -->
            <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9ff 0%, #eef4ff 100%); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(61, 95, 158, 0.15); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); padding: 25px; text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
                <!-- Élément graphique d'arrière-plan -->
                <div style="position: absolute; top: -15px; right: -15px; width: 100px; height: 100px; border-radius: 50%; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(61, 95, 158, 0.08) 0%, rgba(61, 95, 158, 0) 70%);"></div>
                
                <!-- Chiffre principal avec effet visuel -->
                <div style="position: relative; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 5px;">
                    <span style="font-size: 48px; font-weight: 700; color: #3d5f9e; display: block; line-height: 1.2;">{{ pending_modules_count }}</span>
                    <!-- Petite bulle décorative -->
                    <span style="position: absolute; top: -5px; right: -15px; background-color: #ff7b72; color: white; border-radius: 50%; width: 24px; height: 24px; font-size: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">!</span>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Label descriptif -->
                <div style="font-size: 15px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #2c384e; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                    {{ modules_text }} en attente
                </div>
                
                <!-- Séparateur subtil -->
                <div style="width: 40px; height: 3px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(61, 95, 158, 0) 0%, rgba(61, 95, 158, 0.5) 50%, rgba(61, 95, 158, 0) 100%); margin: 15px auto;"></div>
                
                <!-- Information contextuelle avec style -->
                <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #6c757d; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                    <span style="display: inline-block; width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 50%; background-color: #3d5f9e; color: white; margin-right: 8px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 22px;">👤</span>
                    <span>Apprenant : <strong style="color: #2c384e;">{{ owner_fullname }}</strong></span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p class="main-text">
                Nous vous invitons à prendre le temps de consulter et valider ces {{ modules_text }} 
                afin d'accompagner au mieux votre apprenant(e) dans son parcours de formation.
            </p>
            
            <div class="motivation-text">
                💡 Votre accompagnement est essentiel pour la progression et la motivation de {{ owner_fullname }}.
                Chaque validation est une étape importante dans son développement professionnel.
            </div>
            
            <!-- Call to Action -->
            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="{{ path('mentor_dashboard_index', {'nni': mentor_nni}) }}" target="_blank" class="cta-button">
                    🚀 Accéder à mon espace mentor
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <p class="main-text">
                <em>Merci de votre engagement et de votre précieux accompagnement.</em>
            </p>
            
            <!-- Signature -->
            <div class="signature">
                <p>Cordialement,</p>
                <div class="signature-name">L'équipe de gestion des carnets de compagnonnage</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="footer-warning">
                <strong>⚠️ Message automatique</strong><br>
                Ceci est un rappel automatique envoyé chaque mercredi à 14h00.
            </div>
            
            <p>
                <strong>Merci de ne pas répondre directement à cet email.</strong><br>
                Pour toute question ou assistance technique, veuillez contacter notre support.<br><br>
                
                🎯 Destinataire : {{ mentor_email }}
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>